    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts reliably, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While there may be some minor signs of regular use, the interior is clean and the car drives beautifully, making it an excellent choice for anyone looking for a dependable and well-cared-for vehicle.",
